    <p><span>Rogue Mega Evolution, Mega Evolved Pokemon, and Z-A Royale.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Game Freak [273 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/game-freak">Game Freak</a> has released the third official trailer for <em><a title="Games > Pokemon Legends: Z-A [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pokemon-legends-z-a">Pokemon Legends: Z-A</a></em>, which introduces Rogue Mega Evolution and Mega Evolved <a title="Series > Pokemon [44 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/series/pokemon">Pokemon</a>, as well as the Z-A Royale, a new battle mode for Trainers. <span id="more-979403"></span></p><p><em>Pokemon Legends: Z-A</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [249 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a> and Switch 2 on October 16.</p><p>Watch the trailer below. View a new set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/pokemon-legends-z-a/july-22-2025/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Trailer #3</span></h2><p><strong>English: Start a New Story in Lumiose City</strong></p><p><iframe title="[UK] Make the Most of Your Adventure in Pokémon Legends: Z-A!" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VHAcbY1sEag?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
